<paragraph id="825E36B1FFFFF12EFC880E44D1F0A9A7" blockId="11.[811,1457,1363,2028]" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFC880E44D68EA947" box="[813,942,1363,1390]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">Synonymy of</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFC100E43D0ADA947" authority="Morales Agacino, 1949" authorityName="Morales Agacino" authorityYear="1949" box="[949,1421,1363,1390]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mateui">
Pamphagulus mateui 
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFFFF12EFB3B0E43D0ADA947" author="Morales Agacino" box="[1182,1421,1363,1390]" firstAuthor="Morales Agacino" journalOrPublisher="Eos: Revista Espanola de Entomologia" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" pagination="145 - 174" part="25" publicationUrl="http://hdl.handle.net/10261/151226" refId="ref13182" refString="MORALES AGACINO E. 1949. - Mas notas sobre ortopteroides del Sahara Occidental e Ifni. Eos: Revista Espanola de Entomologia 25: 145 - 174. http: // hdl. handle. net / 10261 / 151226" title="Mas notas sobre ortopteroides del Sahara Occidental e Ifni" type="journal article" year="1949">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFB3B0E43D0ADA947" box="[1182,1421,1363,1390]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">Morales Agacino, 1949</emphasis>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFC880E63D1F0A9A7" box="[813,1232,1395,1421]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">
and 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFCFE0E63D1F0A9A7" authority="Ramme, 1931" authorityName="Ramme" authorityYear="1931" box="[859,1232,1395,1421]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicinus">
Pamphagulus vicinus 
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFFFF12EFB9E0E64D1F0A9A7" author="Ramme" box="[1083,1232,1395,1421]" firstAuthor="Ramme" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum Berlin" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" pagination="165 - 200" part="17" refId="ref13685" refString="RAMME W. A. T. 1931. - Beitrage zur Kenntnis der palaearktischen Orthopterenfauna (Tettig. Et Acrid.). Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum Berlin 17: 165 - 200." title="Beitrage zur Kenntnis der palaearktischen Orthopterenfauna (Tettig. Et Acrid.)" type="journal article" year="1931">Ramme, 1931</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="CAFB653AFFFFF129FC880E84D44DA924" lastPageId="12" lastPageNumber="237" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="825E36B1FFFFF12EFC880E84D6C6AB07" blockId="11.[811,1457,1363,2028]" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFFFF12EFC880E84D6CDA984" author="Descamps" box="[813,1005,1427,1454]" firstAuthor="Descamps" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" pagination="24 - 36" part="75" refId="ref11288" refString="DESCAMPS M. 1970. - Contribution a la faune du Maroc. III. Acridoidea du Maroc saharien et Dericorythinae [Orth]. Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France 75 (1 - 2): 24 - 36." title="Contribution a la faune du Maroc. III. Acridoidea du Maroc saharien et Dericorythinae [Orth]." type="journal article" year="1970">Descamps (1970)</bibRefCitation>
compared two paratypes of 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFA800E83D655A9E7" authorityName="Morales Agacino" authorityYear="1949" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mateui">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFA800E83D655A9E7" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">Pamphagulus mateui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with the female type of 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFBD30EA3D645A9C7" authority="Ramme, 1931" authorityName="Ramme" authorityYear="1931" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicinus">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFBD30EA3D06DA9E7" box="[1142,1357,1459,1485]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">Pamphagulus vicinus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFFFF12EFAF10EA3D645A9C7" author="Ramme" firstAuthor="Ramme" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum Berlin" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" pagination="165 - 200" part="17" refId="ref13685" refString="RAMME W. A. T. 1931. - Beitrage zur Kenntnis der palaearktischen Orthopterenfauna (Tettig. Et Acrid.). Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum Berlin 17: 165 - 200." title="Beitrage zur Kenntnis der palaearktischen Orthopterenfauna (Tettig. Et Acrid.)" type="journal article" year="1931">Ramme, 1931</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and studied eight males and three females of 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFAEA0EC4D08FA9C7" authorityName="Ramme" authorityYear="1931" box="[1359,1455,1492,1517]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicinus">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFAEA0EC4D08FA9C7" box="[1359,1455,1492,1517]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">P. vicinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from the Sebkhat Tah preserved at the MNHN. He concluded that 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFC080D02D0A6AA07" authority="Morales Agacino, 1949" authorityName="Morales Agacino" authorityYear="1949" box="[941,1414,1554,1581]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mateui">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFC080D02D1A5AA06" box="[941,1157,1554,1580]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">Pamphagulus mateui</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFFFF12EFB290D02D0A6AA07" author="Morales Agacino" box="[1164,1414,1554,1581]" firstAuthor="Morales Agacino" journalOrPublisher="Eos: Revista Espanola de Entomologia" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" pagination="145 - 174" part="25" publicationUrl="http://hdl.handle.net/10261/151226" refId="ref13182" refString="MORALES AGACINO E. 1949. - Mas notas sobre ortopteroides del Sahara Occidental e Ifni. Eos: Revista Espanola de Entomologia 25: 145 - 174. http: // hdl. handle. net / 10261 / 151226" title="Mas notas sobre ortopteroides del Sahara Occidental e Ifni" type="journal article" year="1949">Morales Agacino, 1949</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFC090D22D03DAA67" authority="Ramme, 1931" authorityName="Ramme" authorityYear="1931" box="[940,1309,1586,1613]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicinus">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFC090D22D1A0AA66" box="[940,1152,1586,1612]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">Pamphagulus vicinus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFFFF12EFB210D23D03DAA67" author="Ramme" box="[1156,1309,1587,1613]" firstAuthor="Ramme" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum Berlin" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" pagination="165 - 200" part="17" refId="ref13685" refString="RAMME W. A. T. 1931. - Beitrage zur Kenntnis der palaearktischen Orthopterenfauna (Tettig. Et Acrid.). Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum Berlin 17: 165 - 200." title="Beitrage zur Kenntnis der palaearktischen Orthopterenfauna (Tettig. Et Acrid.)" type="journal article" year="1931">Ramme, 1931</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
: “(…) aucune différence de nature à justifier des divisions spécifiques n’a pu être relevée. 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFC720D63D118AAA6" authorityName="Ramme" authorityYear="1931" box="[983,1080,1651,1676]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicinus">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFC720D63D118AAA6" box="[983,1080,1651,1676]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">P. vicinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
est cependant très variable quant à la rugosité tégumentaire et l’ampleur de la saillie pronotale.” [(…) no differences that could justify specific divisions could be found. 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFC380DC3D120AAC6" authorityName="Ramme" authorityYear="1931" box="[925,1024,1747,1772]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicinus">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFC380DC3D120AAC6" box="[925,1024,1747,1772]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">P. vicinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is, however, highly variable for integument roughness and for the extent of pronotal projection.] (our translation).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="825E36B1FFFFF129FCE60C21D7A8AFE5" blockId="11.[811,1457,1363,2028]" lastBlockId="12.[131,777,885,1294]" lastPageId="12" lastPageNumber="237" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">
Also, the subspecies, 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFB8E0C21D108AB46" authority="Morales Agacino, 1949" authorityName="Morales Agacino" authorityYear="1949" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="mateui" subSpecies="audebdidetensis">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFB8E0C21D08FAB61" box="[1067,1455,1841,1867]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">Pamphagulus mateui audebdidetensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFFFF12EFC880C41D108AB46" author="Morales Agacino" box="[813,1064,1873,1900]" firstAuthor="Morales Agacino" journalOrPublisher="Eos: Revista Espanola de Entomologia" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" pagination="145 - 174" part="25" publicationUrl="http://hdl.handle.net/10261/151226" refId="ref13182" refString="MORALES AGACINO E. 1949. - Mas notas sobre ortopteroides del Sahara Occidental e Ifni. Eos: Revista Espanola de Entomologia 25: 145 - 174. http: // hdl. handle. net / 10261 / 151226" title="Mas notas sobre ortopteroides del Sahara Occidental e Ifni" type="journal article" year="1949">Morales Agacino, 1949</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, was collected in six localities. In two of these six localities, viz. Bu Kerch and Agli Ben Ali, it was collected the same day with 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFBFC0C82D027AB81" authority="mateui" authorityName="mateui Morales Agacino" authorityYear="1949" box="[1113,1287,1938,1963]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="mateui" subSpecies="mateui">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFBFC0C82D027AB81" box="[1113,1287,1938,1963]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">P. mateui mateui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; it was also collected the same day at Jatuta el Bar with 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFB450CA2D060ABE1" authorityName="Ramme" authorityYear="1931" box="[1248,1344,1970,1995]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicinus">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF12EFB450CA2D060ABE1" box="[1248,1344,1970,1995]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">P. vicinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Table 5). 
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFFFF12EFC890CC2D6C3ABC6" author="Descamps" box="[812,995,2001,2028]" firstAuthor="Descamps" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" pagination="24 - 36" part="75" refId="ref11288" refString="DESCAMPS M. 1970. - Contribution a la faune du Maroc. III. Acridoidea du Maroc saharien et Dericorythinae [Orth]. Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France 75 (1 - 2): 24 - 36." title="Contribution a la faune du Maroc. III. Acridoidea du Maroc saharien et Dericorythinae [Orth]." type="journal article" year="1970">Descamps (1970)</bibRefCitation>
did not raise the issue of 
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFFFF129FB7A0CC1D404AFA5" italics="true" lastPageId="12" lastPageNumber="237" pageId="11" pageNumber="236">
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFFFF12EFB7A0CC1D08FABC1" authorityName="Morales Agacino" authorityYear="1949" box="[1247,1455,2001,2027]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="236" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mateui">Pamphagulus mateui</taxonomicName>
audebdidetensis
</emphasis>
. But mapping the distributions of the three 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFF8F129FF230885D430AF85" authorityName="Uvarov" authorityYear="1929" box="[134,272,917,943]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFF8F129FF230885D430AF85" box="[134,272,917,943]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">Pamphagulus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
taxa shows a consistency between the data of Morales Agacino &amp; Descamps (Fig. 4; Table 5).
</paragraph>
<caption id="D69E6639FFF8F129FF23080BD7FEAF6E" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6573794" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6573794" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6573794/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="237" startId="12.[134,145,795,813]" targetBox="[132,1457,214,752]" targetPageId="12">
<paragraph id="825E36B1FFF8F129FF23080BD7FEAF6E" blockId="12.[134,1456,795,836]" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">
FIG. 3. — Localisation of the locality El Kantara = Al Gantra along the course of Morales Agacino’s 1946 expedition. Symbol: ★, type locality of 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFF8F129FA8B080BD4B4AF6E" authority="Morales Agacino, 1949" authorityName="Morales Agacino" authorityYear="1949" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Bolivaremia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="domenechi">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFF8F129FA8B080BD5EDAF6E" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">Bolivaremia domenechi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFF8F129FF770822D4B4AF6E" author="Morales Agacino" box="[210,404,818,836]" firstAuthor="Morales Agacino" pageId="12" pageNumber="237" pagination="145 - 174" refId="ref13182" refString="MORALES AGACINO E. 1949. - Mas notas sobre ortopteroides del Sahara Occidental e Ifni. Eos: Revista Espanola de Entomologia 25: 145 - 174. http: // hdl. handle. net / 10261 / 151226" type="journal article" year="1949">Morales Agacino, 1949</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. Modified from 
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFF8F129FDB00822D7FAAF6E" author="Map of Morocco" box="[533,730,817,836]" firstAuthor="Map of Morocco" pageId="12" pageNumber="237" pagination="1993" refId="ref12608" refString="MAP OF MOROCCO 1993. - Topographic map, scale: 1 / 250,000. Leaflet: NG 28 edition 1993. DCCCDC Morocco, Rabat 1993." type="journal article" year="1993">Map of Morocco (1993)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="825E36B1FFF8F129FF3E08C5D44DA924" blockId="12.[131,777,885,1294]" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">
On the basis of these distributional data, the synonymy of the two subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFF8F129FE3C08E5D4DCA824" authorityName="Morales Agacino" authorityYear="1949" box="[409,508,1013,1038]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mateui">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFF8F129FE3C08E5D4DCA824" box="[409,508,1013,1038]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">P. mateui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should be reconsidered, as they occur together in the same collecting sites. In the same way, the examination of the specimens collected by Morales Agacino should help considering if 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFF8F129FDFF0F45D79AA844" authorityName="Morales Agacino" authorityYear="1949" box="[602,698,1109,1134]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mateui">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFF8F129FDFF0F45D79AA844" box="[602,698,1109,1134]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">P. mateui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should be synonymized with 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFF8F129FED20F65D4FAA8A4" authorityName="Ramme" authorityYear="1931" box="[375,474,1141,1166]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicinus">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFF8F129FED20F65D4FAA8A4" box="[375,474,1141,1166]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">P. vicinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as suggested by 
<bibRefCitation id="E6704B40FFF8F129FD3D0F65D5F1A884" author="Descamps" firstAuthor="Descamps" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France" pageId="12" pageNumber="237" pagination="24 - 36" part="75" refId="ref11288" refString="DESCAMPS M. 1970. - Contribution a la faune du Maroc. III. Acridoidea du Maroc saharien et Dericorythinae [Orth]. Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France 75 (1 - 2): 24 - 36." title="Contribution a la faune du Maroc. III. Acridoidea du Maroc saharien et Dericorythinae [Orth]." type="journal article" year="1970">Descamps (1970)</bibRefCitation>
: a single species, 
<taxonomicName id="45E14D32FFF8F129FE2C0F84D743A884" authorityName="Ramme" authorityYear="1931" box="[393,611,1172,1198]" class="Insecta" family="Dericorythidae" genus="Pamphagulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicinus">
<emphasis id="B095EAA3FFF8F129FE2C0F84D743A884" box="[393,611,1172,1198]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">Pamphagulus vicinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, could actually be present along the coast of Atlantic Sahara from the Sebkhat Tah (27°40’N, 12°48’W) to the Cap Blanc peninsula (21°06’N, 17°03’W).
</paragraph>
